<p>The same can be used for the <code class="highlighter-rouge">mv</code> command which will also be in <code class="highlighter-rouge">src</code>, however, give preference to the <code class="highlighter-rouge">-g</code> parameter instead of the <del><code class="highlighter-rouge">--progress-bar</code></del>, it is simpler! But honestly, I donâ€™t see any use in using this in <code class="highlighter-rouge">mv</code> because things are moved so fast that you donâ€™t even need it.</p>

<p>Thatâ€™s it for today!</p>

